segment.source: You can review event IDs in the Event Viewer on individual endpoints.
segment.target: You can review event IDs in the Event Viewer on individual endpoints.

segment.source: For example, if endpoints are not appearing in the Machines view list, you might need to look for event IDs on the endpoints.
segment.target: For example, if endpoints are not appearing in the Machines view list, you might need to look for event IDs on the endpoints.

segment.source: You can then use this table to determine further troubleshooting steps.
segment.target: You can then use this table to determine further troubleshooting steps.

segment.source: Note It can take several days for endpoints to begin reporting to the Windows Defender ATP service.
segment.target: Note It can take several days for endpoints to begin reporting to the Windows Defender ATP service.

segment.source: Open Event Viewer and find the Windows Defender ATP service event log:
segment.target: Open Event Viewer and find the Windows Defender ATP service event log:

segment.source: Click Start, type Event Viewer, and press Enter.
segment.target: Click Start, type Event Viewer, and press Enter.

segment.source: In the log list, under Log Summary, scroll until you see Microsoft-Windows-SENSE/Operational.
segment.target: In the log list, under Log Summary, scroll until you see Microsoft-Windows-SENSE/Operational.

segment.source: Double-click the item to open the log.
segment.target: Double-click the item to open the log.

segment.source: a.
segment.target: a.

segment.source: You can also access the log by expanding Applications and Services LogsMicrosoftWindowsSENSE and click on Operational.
segment.target: You can also access the log by expanding Applications and Services LogsMicrosoftWindowsSENSE and click on Operational.

segment.source: Note SENSE is the internal name used to refer to the behavioral sensor that powers Windows Defender ATP.
segment.target: Note SENSE is the internal name used to refer to the behavioral sensor that powers Windows Defender ATP.
